Author: HolisticlyImprobable
Text: Sometimes when you're looking at other people's experiences with an ED it feels like you're not as "good" (one as good at starving) as them, I know I've felt it. But you don't have to be, although it can be involuntary this is not someplace you have to compare yourself against, this is support and acceptance and understanding. We care and we love.  I don't know you or what you've already done. But remember you deserve to be happy no matter what. And you deserve to be able to use antiseptics and plasters to clean up if you have cut. This is all fucked but at least we're fucked together xxx
